### Step 1: Create the entry with JSON metadata
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/controller/MediaFile
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "mediaType": "pdf",
    "filename": "MyTest.pdf"
}

### Step 2: Upload the binary stream via PUT to the media property
### (Adjust 'content' to match the LargeBinary/Stream property name in your data-model.cds)
PUT http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/controller/MediaFile('af16e414-5b87-4ed3-bb9c-2b6b9103c093')/content
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../srv/test.pdf